mesquite.lib.characters

Interface MCharactersHistory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Annotatable, Listable, MAdjustableDistribution, MCharactersDistribution, MCharactersStatesHolder, Renamable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MCategoricalHistory, MContinuousHistory, MDNAHistory, MMeristicHistory, MProteinHistory

    public interface MCharactersHistory
extends MAdjustableDistribution
    Stores the reconstructed or simulated states at each of the nodes of a tree, for each of many characters. See general discussion of character storage classes under CharacterState
